1. Igrali smo *bejzbol* na igralištu. (We played baseball at the playground.)
2. *Bejzbol* je popularan sport u Americi. (Baseball is a popular sport in America.)
3. Ovaj šešir je s logom *bejzbol* kluba. (This hat has the logo of a baseball club.)
4. Naš tim je pobedio na *bejzbol* takmičenju. (Our team won at the baseball competition.)
5. Učili smo o istoriji *bejzbola* na času istorije. (We learned about the history of baseball in history class.)
6. Mog brata zanima *bejzbol* i redovno ga gleda na televiziji. (My brother is interested in baseball and regularly watches it on TV.)
7. *Bejzbol* loptica je okrugla i bela sa crvenim šavovima. (A baseball is round and white with red seams.)
8. Oni su igrali *bejzbol* na plaži prošlog vikenda. (They played baseball on the beach last weekend.)
9. Moramo kupiti nove *bejzbol* rukavice za sledeću sezonu. (We need to buy new baseball gloves for the next season.)
10. Posetili smo *bejzbol* muzej tokom našeg putovanja u Njujork. (We visited the baseball museum during our trip to New York.)